1
00:00:25,840 --> 00:00:26,320
Hello.

2
00:00:26,680 --> 00:00:28,760
Hello. Is this Li Xuebo's house?

3
00:00:28,760 --> 00:00:30,600
Yes. Are you my son's friend?

4
00:00:30,680 --> 00:00:31,840
Come in.

5
00:00:32,880 --> 00:00:34,080
The things my son asked me to prepare,

6
00:00:34,080 --> 00:00:35,000
I have already prepared them.

7
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:36,560
Please give them to him.

8
00:00:36,840 --> 00:00:39,100
The things your son asked you to prepare?

9
00:00:40,160 --> 00:00:41,520
What is this?

10
00:00:41,520 --> 00:00:42,200
Look.

11
00:00:46,040 --> 00:00:47,040
So much money.

12
00:00:47,080 --> 00:00:47,960
How much is it?

13
00:00:48,240 --> 00:00:49,640
Three hundred thousand.

14
00:00:50,640 --> 00:00:51,840
Did your son contact you

15
00:00:51,840 --> 00:00:53,400
and ask you to prepare this much money?

16
00:00:53,400 --> 00:00:55,130
Right. When did he contact you?

17
00:00:55,280 --> 00:00:56,080
Yesterday.

18
00:00:57,000 --> 00:00:59,240
Yesterday. Did he say anything else?

19
00:00:59,600 --> 00:01:01,000
He said after I get it ready,

20
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:02,360
his friend would come to pick it up.

21
00:01:02,360 --> 00:01:04,560
Aren't you his friend?

22
00:01:04,760 --> 00:01:06,480
Then do you know where my son is now?

23
00:01:06,480 --> 00:01:07,560
What exactly happened?

24
00:01:07,560 --> 00:01:08,320
Who are you?

25
00:01:08,640 --> 00:01:10,170
There's no time to explain.

26
00:01:10,640 --> 00:01:11,880
Can I use this phone?

27
00:01:12,200 --> 00:01:12,880
Yes.

28
00:01:15,680 --> 00:01:16,410
Don't panic.

29
00:01:19,880 --> 00:01:21,680
Is this Dongwan Criminal Investigation Detachment?

30
00:01:21,680 --> 00:01:23,760
I'm Ma Guodong from Guangnan Criminal Investigation Detachment.

31
00:01:23,760 --> 00:01:25,039
Please contact Comrade Lin Wei

32
00:01:25,039 --> 00:01:28,039
and ask him to come to Room 303, Building 2, City Garden.

33
00:01:28,039 --> 00:01:29,039
Yes, requesting backup.

34
00:01:29,039 --> 00:01:30,600
Hurry, as soon as possible.

35
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:31,360
Officer,

36
00:01:31,360 --> 00:01:31,960
what should I do?

37
00:01:31,960 --> 00:01:33,490
He didn't answer my call...

38
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:04,040
Coming, coming, coming.

39
00:02:08,919 --> 00:02:11,160
Are you Li Xuebo's family?

40
00:02:11,160 --> 00:02:12,520
I'm Xuebo's father.

41
00:02:14,440 --> 00:02:15,760
Are the things ready?

42
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:16,560
Xuebo told me.

43
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:17,400
They are ready.

44
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:18,120
We were just waiting for you.

45
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:19,520
Come on, come in, come in.

46
00:02:26,320 --> 00:02:28,440
That brat Xuebo called me yesterday

47
00:02:28,440 --> 00:02:29,120
and asked me to prepare money.

48
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:30,320
Where was I supposed to get that much money?

49
00:02:30,320 --> 00:02:31,320
I just got it ready

50
00:02:31,320 --> 00:02:33,050
and waited for you to pick it up.

51
00:02:35,320 --> 00:02:36,760
You look a bit familiar.

52
00:02:38,320 --> 00:02:39,640
I just have a common face.

53
00:02:39,640 --> 00:02:42,120
The streets are full of old men like me.

54
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,720
Here, take a look at the stuff.

55
00:02:43,720 --> 00:02:45,380
I'll pour you a glass of water.

56
00:02:49,120 --> 00:02:50,160
Do you smoke?

57
00:02:52,440 --> 00:02:53,920
I used to.

58
00:02:54,160 --> 00:02:55,920
Got a light, buddy?

59
00:02:56,320 --> 00:02:57,120
A Zippo.

60
00:02:58,200 --> 00:02:59,040
It's fake.

61
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:02,320
Actually, a real Zippo isn't expensive either.

62
00:03:02,320 --> 00:03:05,000
Ask your girlfriend to buy you a real one.

63
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:06,640
Later, my health got worse,

64
00:03:06,640 --> 00:03:07,720
and Xuebo wouldn't let me smoke,

65
00:03:07,720 --> 00:03:08,640
so I quit.

66
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:11,920
My girlfriend replaced it with a real Zippo for me.

67
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:13,600
I want to lend it to you again.

68
00:03:14,320 --> 00:03:15,720
What is a Zippo?

69
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:27,579
Where is the money?

70
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:31,060
I don't have any money.

71
00:03:31,320 --> 00:03:32,650
But you can have my life.

72
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:50,240
Are you Li Xuebo's father?

73
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:53,180
Where's the money?

74
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:56,720
Take it out.

75
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:59,720
Hurry up.

76
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:59,560
Ma, Ma, speak to me.

77
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:00,840
I'm alive.

78
00:05:00,840 --> 00:05:02,370
What are you yelling about?

79
00:05:04,480 --> 00:05:06,440
Well, I...

80
00:05:06,560 --> 00:05:08,600
I don't have much time left anyway.

81
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:09,930
Careful, he's got a gun.

82
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:11,730
Should we shoot?

83
00:05:12,760 --> 00:05:14,960
Hua Weihong, don't do anything stupid.

84
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:16,040
You can't get away anyway.

85
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:17,040
Throw the gun out.

86
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:22,260
If I told you to throw your gun, would you?

87
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:24,560
Let me tell you,

88
00:05:24,640 --> 00:05:26,600
I'm here to put my life on the line today.

89
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:28,480
You can't afford to play this game.

90
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:29,840
We can't afford to play.

91
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:31,440
So we won't play.

92
00:05:31,640 --> 00:05:32,900
Life is very precious.

93
00:05:35,159 --> 00:05:36,640
Life is precious.

94
00:05:36,840 --> 00:05:38,760
How much do you earn a month?

95
00:05:38,760 --> 00:05:41,290
And you're talking to me about preciousness?

96
00:05:53,760 --> 00:05:54,760
All right, all right.

97
00:05:54,760 --> 00:05:56,240
You are all precious, okay?

98
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:57,760
Let's not talk about preciousness.

99
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:58,880
Let's talk.

100
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:00,280
Cao Aiyuan.

101
00:06:00,960 --> 00:06:01,880
I don't know.

102
00:06:15,640 --> 00:06:17,560
Why didn't you hit my head?

103
00:06:59,640 --> 00:07:01,300
I feel like he won't come back.

104
00:07:01,960 --> 00:07:02,760
Meijuan,

105
00:07:03,880 --> 00:07:05,040
let me go.

106
00:07:09,760 --> 00:07:10,960
I'm sorry, Xuebo.

107
00:07:12,080 --> 00:07:12,880
I lied to you,

108
00:07:14,520 --> 00:07:15,760
but I was forced.

109
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:20,960
It's fine.

110
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:26,840
I don't care if you're Cao Aiyuan or Liu Meijuan,

111
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:29,200
I love you.

112
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:32,490
We even have a child now.

113
00:07:35,080 --> 00:07:36,040
The three of us

114
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:38,560
will live a good life,

115
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:40,280
okay?

116
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:45,320
But I'm not sure if the child is yours.

117
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:48,840
I don't care.

118
00:07:50,760 --> 00:07:52,960
I don't care what kind of person you are,

119
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:54,600
or whose child it is,

120
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:57,880
I accept it all.

121
00:08:04,840 --> 00:08:06,320
Can I trust you?

122
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:08,360
Of course.

123
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:16,360
You said you'd take me to many places,

124
00:08:17,480 --> 00:08:18,680
was that true?

125
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:20,170
Of course it's true.

126
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:24,410
Let's leave here

127
00:08:26,200 --> 00:08:27,460
and turn ourselves in.

128
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:29,160
When you get out,

129
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:29,960
I'll take you

130
00:08:31,280 --> 00:08:32,360
and our child

131
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:35,280
wherever you want.

132
00:08:37,559 --> 00:08:38,240
But

133
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:42,530
if I turn myself in, I won't get out.

134
00:08:43,039 --> 00:08:44,570
How could that be, Meijuan?

135
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:47,440
It's just a kidnapping case.

136
00:08:48,800 --> 00:08:50,280
I'll tell the police

137
00:08:51,640 --> 00:08:53,040
that you were forced too,

138
00:08:53,040 --> 00:08:54,640
there won't be a big problem.

139
00:08:57,880 --> 00:08:59,360
Even if you're sentenced

140
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:03,360
to one, three, or even five years,

141
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:04,240
I'll wait for you.

142
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:05,700
I've also killed someone.

143
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:12,220
Are you scared?

144
00:09:16,160 --> 00:09:17,160
No.

145
00:09:18,040 --> 00:09:19,570
How could I be scared of you,

146
00:09:20,160 --> 00:09:20,960
Meijuan?

147
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:23,480
Let me go.

148
00:09:24,280 --> 00:09:26,210
I won't say anything to the police.

149
00:09:28,360 --> 00:09:29,160
You lied to me.

150
00:09:31,760 --> 00:09:33,360
I didn't lie to you, Meijuan,

151
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:35,400
really.

152
00:09:37,880 --> 00:09:38,840
Let me go.

153
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:41,260
I can pretend I don't know you,

154
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:43,600
like we never met.

155
00:09:44,560 --> 00:09:46,020
I can give up the child too,

156
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:47,960
just let me go.

157
00:10:01,160 --> 00:10:01,600
Okay.

158
00:10:07,560 --> 00:10:09,040
Can you do me a favor then?

159
00:10:09,520 --> 00:10:10,200
Yes.

160
00:10:12,480 --> 00:10:14,480
You need money to leave here, right?

161
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:16,360
Let me leave,

162
00:10:16,640 --> 00:10:18,440
I'll give you as much as you need.

163
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:26,800
Lin Wei.

164
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:33,800
No way. Was Hua Weihong's punch that heavy?

165
00:10:34,520 --> 00:10:35,400
Stomachache.

166
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:37,760
Is it serious?

167
00:10:38,560 --> 00:10:40,420
Let me go to the hospital with you.

168
00:10:47,280 --> 00:10:48,560
It's an old problem.

169
00:10:49,160 --> 00:10:50,090
Stomach cancer.

170
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:51,930
Are you serious?

171
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:53,840
Of course.

172
00:10:53,880 --> 00:10:56,280
Then why didn't you go see a doctor earlier?

173
00:10:58,160 --> 00:10:58,800
I told you.

174
00:10:58,800 --> 00:11:00,260
But you didn't believe me.

175
00:11:00,400 --> 00:11:03,660
I took sick leave last time to get a checkup at the hospital.

176
00:11:08,560 --> 00:11:09,480
Alright.

177
00:11:10,840 --> 00:11:12,440
Hua Weihong has been caught.

178
00:11:13,160 --> 00:11:15,220
I'll leave the interrogation to you.

179
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:20,240
I'll hurry to the hospital

180
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:21,500
and get checked again.

181
00:11:24,840 --> 00:11:26,640
Go get checked at the hospital early.

182
00:11:26,640 --> 00:11:27,680
Come back and get your cigarettes after the checkup.

183
00:11:27,680 --> 00:11:28,400
Kid.

184
00:11:29,080 --> 00:11:30,680
You are quite nosy.

185
00:11:43,560 --> 00:11:44,360
Lao Ma.

186
00:11:45,760 --> 00:11:46,480
I'm sorry.

187
00:11:49,760 --> 00:11:51,960
Come back early to get your cigarettes.

188
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:52,840
Wait for me.
